  <title>我的网站换上了新主题</title>
  <link>https://www.kayak4665664.com/zh-cn/my-website-has-a-new-theme/</link>
  <pubDate>Mon, 27 Feb 2023 19:08:08 &#43;0800</pubDate>
  <author>kayak4665664</author>
  <guid>https://www.kayak4665664.com/zh-cn/my-website-has-a-new-theme/</guid>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>自从2021年建立我的网站以来，我一直都在用<a href="https://github.com/dillonzq/LoveIt"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">LoveIt<i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>这个Hugo主题，没太大变化。这一次，我迁移到了<a href="https://github.com/hugo-fixit/FixIt"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">FixIt<i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>主题，不仅修复了LoveIt中的一些问题，也带来了更多新功能和优化，顺便也把评论系统从<a href="https://valine.js.org/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Valine<i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>迁移到了<a href="https://waline.js.org/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Waline<i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>。</p>
